import React from 'react'
import Header from './Header'
import Leftbar from './Leftbar'
import Navbar from './Navbar'
import Card from './Card'

export default function Dashboard() {




  return (
    <>

      {/* <Header /> */}
      <Navbar />
      <Leftbar />
      {/* <Card /> */}
      <Grid container spacing={2}>
        <Grid item xs={3}>
          <Item>xs=8</Item>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={3}>
          <Item>xs=8</Item>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>


    </>
  )
}
